  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to a high heat, then boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>(For a more interesting texture) rip the <strong>portobello </strong>and<strong> chestnut&nbsp;mushrooms</strong>&nbsp;into bite-sized pieces onto a baking tray, drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong>&nbsp;then season generously with<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the tray directly under the grill and cook for 12-15 min or until they're nicely caramelised</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>3 seed mix</strong> to a large pot&nbsp;over a high heat and cook for 1-2 min or until toasted</p>\r\n<p>Once toasted, set aside on a plate and keep the pot for later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pot to a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> linguine</strong> with plenty of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-12 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, drain and reserve a cup of the<strong> starchy cooking water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chop the<strong> basil</strong> finely, including the stalks&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> finely&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grind the<strong> chopped</strong>&nbsp;<strong>basil</strong>, <strong>chopped&nbsp;</strong><strong>garlic</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> in a <strong>pestle &amp; mortar</strong> to form a smooth paste</p>\r\n<p>Add 2-3 tbsp<strong> olive oil</strong> and mix well</p>\r\n<p>Tip: if you don't have a pestle and mortar, chop the basil very finely, then mix with olive oil</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>grated cheese</strong> to the <strong>basil</strong> with 2-3 tbsp<strong> olive oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix thoroughly &ndash; this is your <strong>pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the drained <strong>linguine</strong> to the pot with a splash of your reserved <strong>starchy cooking water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Stir the <strong>pesto</strong> and half of the <strong>caramelised</strong>&nbsp;<strong>mushrooms</strong>&nbsp;through and cook for 1 min or until the pesto has coated the pasta and the cheese has melted&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/826.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> linguine</strong> in bowls and garnish with the <strong>toasted 3 seed mix</strong></p>\r\n<p>Top with the remaining<strong> caramelised&nbsp;mushrooms</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
